{"tid":2381253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人妻驚見丈夫與年輕女人同遊合照　怒斬「偷食夫」後始知點錯相","createTime":"2021-01-26T12:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T12:38:07.000Z","uid":36494,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c8508feab4603bb7cfd19d3121f244f5f2eefd00","tid":2381253,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T12:15:56.000Z","msg":"兩夫妻相處講求信任，日前墨西哥一名妻子因吃醋刺傷丈夫。墨西哥人妻Leonora日前<span class=\"red\">偷看丈夫Juan手機，發現丈夫手機有數張與年輕女人同遊的合照，以為他出軌，憤而用刀刺傷丈夫。</span><br />\n<br />\n事件發生在本月22日，丈夫Juan被刺傷之後，試圖奪去Leonora手上的刀，並向她解釋手機中的相片是兩人昔日的合照。Juan指兩人拍拖同遊的照片是以菲林拍攝，近日他將相片數碼化並儲存在手機內，方便翻看。<span class=\"red\">Leonora在相中看到年輕貌美的女子，並不是第三者，而是多年前的自己</span>。<br />\n<br />\n事發時鄰居聽到慘叫聲，於是幫忙報警。Juan身上有多處刀傷，Leonora因傷人被當地警方拘捕。"},{"pid":"11baefdfbccdadfd2c3e709189eee9b54cf17735","tid":2381253,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T12:16:22.000Z","msg":"圖？"},{"pid":"dfa7d4e2ac15c3b6f8bd17519dc596ce40744bfa","tid":2381253,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11baefdfbccdadfd2c3e709189eee9b54cf17735","tid":2381253,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T12:16:22.000Z","msg":"圖？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T12:17:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2861856/%E3%80%90%E9%86%8B%E5%A6%BB%E6%96%AC%E5%A4%AB%E3%80%91%E4%BA%BA%E5%A6%BB%E9%A9%9A%E8%A6%8B%E4%B8%88%E5%A4%AB%E8%88%87%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E5%A5%B3%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%8C%E9%81%8A%E5%90%88%E7%85%A7%E3%80%80%E6%80%92%E6%96%AC%E3%80%8C%E5%81%B7%E9%A3%9F%E5%A4%AB%E3%80%8D%E5%BE%8C%E5%A7%8B%E7%9F%A5%E9%BB%9E%E9%8C%AF%E7%9B%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2861856%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2586%258B%25E5%25A6%25BB%25E6%2596%25AC%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A6%25BB%25E9%25A9%259A%25E8%25A6%258B%25E4%25B8%2588%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2590%258C%25E9%2581%25